(b) in point (6), point (b) is replaced by the following:
‘(b) in the case of trusts, all following persons:
(i) the settlor(s);
(ii) the trustee(s);
(iii) the protector(s), if any;
(iv) the beneficiaries or where the individuals benefiting from the legal arrangement or entity have yet to be
